{"tid":1605092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法球迷不滿賽會迎合中国市場　砌巨型藏獨旗報復","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:33:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e03871b0f4209e7306607d89e781ba3c8dda9fb","tid":1605092,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190930/photo/bkn-20190930145729875-0930_00882_001_01p.jpg?20190930151743\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190930%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190930145729875-0930_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20190930151743&h=97f06351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人認為「體育無關政治」，但事實係唔係咁呢？法國人就話你聽佢哋諗法。法甲勁旅里昂於本月28號對南特，於看台赫然出現由球迷排成、代表西藏獨立運動嘅「雪山獅子旗」。法甲賽會為迎合中國市場，將包括今戰嘅部份法甲賽事提早到當地時間中午進行，里昂球迷對呢個安排非常不滿，故砌出「藏獨」旗幟「報復」中國。<br />\n<br />\n為咗推廣法甲、迎合中國嘅龐大市場，法國足總決定將某啲賽事嘅開賽時間提早，里昂對南特呢場波，就於周六被改為中午1點半開波。據當地傳媒報道，里昂Fans對迎開波時間非常唔習慣，對賽會掛住搵錢，唔理本地球迷感受勁不滿，所以決定將矛頭指向中國。除咗砌出極大嘅「雪山獅子旗」外，唔少球迷仲手持相同旗幟喺場上揮舞。中國球迷於看直播嘅時候，必定會睇到相關情況。 <br />\n<br />\n據法國傳媒報道，球迷組職負責人表示，今次行動係故意令中國難堪，佢哋認為當地球迷感受先係最重要，所以用呢個行動向中國示威。另外佢哋強調，若賽會冇跟進相關問題，之後將會繼續「砌旗」同舉藏獨旗幟。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190930/photo/bkn-20190930145729875-0930_00882_001_02p.jpg?20190930151743\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190930%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190930145729875-0930_00882_001_02p.jpg%3F20190930151743&h=cfeeca79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190930/bkn-20190930145729875-0930_00882_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f2f9a6e459b64d35645d96296252fc9e028f08d7","tid":1605092,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"WE Connect"},{"pid":"14494e1964ca07e60ab97911e9f32ec8dc8beee0","tid":1605092,"uid":1989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:32:27.000Z","msg":"支那垃圾<br />\n神憎鬼厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37682fcc9f73b8c2f0da7d31afe768a242776d58","tid":1605092,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"「TaiwanWarmPower」今晚（15日）在臉書發文，呼籲民眾一同連署「德國聯邦議會第95643號請願書」 ，支持「請求德國與中華民國（台灣）建立外交關係」，內文中指出迫害人權的中共不應代表民主自由的台灣。小編表示，可參考連署教學影片，2分鐘左右的時間就能完成簽署，如能在10月9日前達成5萬人連署，就有機會將此議題送進德國國會。<br />\n<br />\n#AntiChinazi<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2916703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2916703&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Znr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=1c4ef536\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2916703&h=2efc4681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2916703</a><br />\n<br />\n連署教學from TW:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/allen.taiwangermany/videos/pcb.2942668175748064/2942643702417178/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fallen.taiwangermany%2Fvideos%2Fpcb.2942668175748064%2F2942643702417178%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Znr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=345619bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/allen.taiwangermany/videos/pcb.2942668175748064/2942643702417178/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n連署link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_05/_31/Petition_95643.mitzeichnen.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_05%2F_31%2FPetition_95643.mitzeichnen.html&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Znr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=d25a32c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_05/_31/Petition_95643.mitzeichnen.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家幫下手, 聯台灣抗邪惡強国<br />\n<br />\n仲爭萬一咋"}]}